<div class="numbered">
The type aliases `atomic_intN_t`, `atomic_uintN_t`, `atomic_intptr_t`, and `atomic_uintptr_t` are defined if and only if `intN_t`, `uintN_t`, `intptr_t`, and `uintptr_t` are defined, respectively.
